headline: Southwest Airlines upgrade, Starbucks downgrade: Trending Tickers
summary: Southwest Airlines (LUV) received an upgrade to a Buy rating from Deutsche Bank analysts, citing the stock upside tied to Elliott Management's stake in the airway operator. Starbucks (SBUX) shares were downgraded to Hold by the team at TD Cowen. Wealth host Brad Smith and Yahoo Finance senior reporter Allie Canal dive deep into these trending stocks on the Yahoo Finance platform. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Wealth here.
